fields.label: Blocks
fields.name: blocks
fields.instructions:
Anchors:
- Must be unique to the page
- All lowercase
- No symbols
- No spaces
For example if a section is called "Who are we", the anchor ID could be "who-are-we". To link to a scroll to ID, add the ID to the end of the URL along with a hash (https://peninsulagarde.wpengine.com#who-are-we)

sub_fields.label: About this block
sub_fields.message:
This block will automatically display images from the Peninsula Gardens instagram account.
Please note that in order to change the Instagram account, a new API key will need to be obtained and for this you will need to contact this site's developers.
This block will break if the Instagram account's password or handle changes, or if Meta updates their terms of service. If this happens, please contact this site's developers who can re-activate it for you.
